  <description type="morphology">Stems to 2 cm, slender and wiry, in dense tufts.  Leaves densely imbricate, not fragile, channeled and incurved when dry, scarcely spreading when moist; not constricted at junction of sheath and blade, the blade persistent, sheath broadly elliptic; marginal lamina typically entire, or finely and remotely serrate toward the tip.  Capsule small and subglobose.</description>
